1118
01:12:40,428 --> 01:12:46,302
- I think that we like to keep our options
open, but it's silly to risk arrest

1119
01:12:46,302 --> 01:12:50,058
and the hassles that are tended upon
and if you can get serious attention

1120
01:12:50,058 --> 01:12:52,949
and negotiations going
with other measures.

1121
01:12:53,927 --> 01:12:57,776
- We've just released a report,
