1179
01:15:59,063 --> 01:16:02,386
If you want something to be done,
you ask me a question and you listen.

1180
01:16:02,386 --> 01:16:05,253
If you don’t agree with me,
go support somebody else for president,

1181
01:16:05,253 --> 01:16:06,997
but quit talking to me like that.

1182
01:16:06,997 --> 01:16:10,459
This is not a matter of personal attack,
