01:23:23,662 --> 01:23:28,337
I can't tell you where it's coming from,
but I am very much concerned about AIDS.

1250
01:23:28,337 --> 01:23:31,975
And I believe that we've got the
best researchers in the world

1251
01:23:31,975 --> 01:23:34,437
out there at NIH working the problem.

1252
01:23:34,437 --> 01:23:37,656
<i>It's one of the few disease</i>
where behavior matters.

