01:24:44,278 --> 01:24:48,759
<i>but so we could celebrate</i>
his undying anger.

1264
01:24:50,192 --> 01:24:53,690
<i>This isn't a political funeral</i>
for Mark.

1265
01:24:53,690 --> 01:24:57,721
It's a political funeral
for the man who killed him,

1266
01:24:58,059 --> 01:25:02,926
and so many others
