1268
01:25:08,106 --> 01:25:13,544
George Bush, we believe
you'll be defeated tomorrow,

1269
01:25:13,544 --> 01:25:17,616
because we believe there's still
some justice left in the universe,

1270
01:25:17,616 --> 01:25:22,136
and some compassion left
in the American people.

1271
01:25:22,853 --> 01:25:29,270
