longer speak, the dead may speak for them.

1277
01:25:59,258 --> 01:26:05,213
<i>Mark's voice is here with us,</i>
as is the voice of Pericles,

1278
01:26:05,618 --> 01:26:10,594
who two millenniums ago, mourned 
the Athenian soldiers

1279
01:26:10,594 --> 01:26:14,614
who didn't have to die 
and in whose death he was complicit.

1280
01:26:15,092 --> 01:26:21,265
But who had an ability to say
that their memorial was the whole earth.

1281
01:26:21,848 --> 01:26:29,330
Let the whole earth hear us now.
We beg, we pray, we demand!

1282
01:26:29,584 --> 01:26:33,136
That this epidemic end!

1283
01:26:33,235 --> 01:26:42,606
Not just so we may live, but so that
Mark's soul may rest in peace at last.

1284
01:26:48,437 --> 01:26:54,505
And in anger and in grief, this fight 
is not over until all of us is safe.

1285
01:27:02,401 --> 01:27:06,599
ACT UP, fight back, fight AIDS.

